  "text": "A total of 2,288 confirmed measles cases were reported in the United States during 2025, with 48 outbreaks reported and 90% of confirmed cases (2,065 of 2,288) being outbreak-associated. The best way to protect yourself against measles is with the measles, mumps, and rubella (MMR) vaccine.",
